essions_list, the cron sessions are all still running as expected, with ed2d0b5d, 6f3323ef, and e7885813 active and updated in the last few minutes.\\n\\nThe telegram sessions show the group channel for -5163901258 is still running since 11:56 UTC, the group for -5168104492 finished around 06:42 UTC, and the direct telegram channel ended at 12:02 UTC. The two zombie cron sessions remain unchanged. The pipeline is stable with no new failures, blockers, or alerts detected, so I'm staying silent on this.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Comparing current session state (13:51 UTC) against heartbeat state (13:36 UTC):\\n\\n**All sessions stable — no changes detected.**\\n\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) — still running ✅\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) — still running ✅\\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) — still running ✅\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` — still running ✅\\n- `telegram:group:-5168104492` — still done (since 10:55 UTC) ✅\\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` — still done (since 13:15 UTC) ✅\\n- Pre-existing zombie crons (`b653a6c0`, `ac986a8d`) — unchanged ✅\\n\\nNo new failures. No blockers. Silent exit.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 30159,\n            \"output\": 520,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45041,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 418,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776174737267,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d79929332e30061ef77a30a176a0e\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"266d6eb9\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\